      "blocks": {
        "text_block_g7kewi": {
          "type": "text_block",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Returns Policy</p>",
            "font_family": "sans_serif_n4",
            "font_size": 30,
            "font_size_mobile": 16,
            "font_weight": "700",
            "text_color": "#727272",
            "letter_spacing": 0,
            "word_spacing": 1,
            "text_alignment": "left",
            "margin_bottom": 30
          }
        },
        "text_block_MX7GTd": {
          "type": "text_block",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>We strive to ensure that all our products reach you in perfect condition. However, we accept returns under the following conditions:</p><ul><li>The product is <strong>damaged, defective, or incorrect</strong> at the time of delivery</li><li>The return request is raised within <strong>3–5 days of delivery</strong></li><li>The product is <strong>unused, unopened, and in original packaging</strong></li></ul>",
            "font_family": "sans_serif_n4",
            "font_size": 20,
            "font_size_mobile": 16,
            "font_weight": "500",
            "text_color": "#727272",
            "letter_spacing": 0,
            "word_spacing": 1,
            "text_alignment": "left",
            "margin_bottom": 30
          }
        },
        "text_block_Qr7Vt3": {
          "type": "text_block",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>     <strong>Non-Returnable Items:</strong></p><ul><li>Used or opened products</li><li>Products damaged due to misuse or mishandling</li><li>Items returned without original packaging</li></ul>",
            "font_family": "sans_serif_n4",
            "font_size": 20,
            "font_size_mobile": 16,
            "font_weight": "500",
            "text_color": "#727272",
            "letter_spacing": 0,
            "word_spacing": 1,
            "text_alignment": "left",
            "margin_bottom": 30
          }
        },
        "text_block_CTEQwQ": {
          "type": "text_block",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Return Process</p>",
            "font_family": "sans_serif_n4",
            "font_size": 30,
            "font_size_mobile": 16,
            "font_weight": "700",
            "text_color": "#727272",
            "letter_spacing": 0,
            "word_spacing": 1,
            "text_alignment": "left",
            "margin_bottom": 30
          }
        },
        "text_block_jiUhaf": {
          "type": "text_block",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>To initiate a return:</p><ol><li>Email us at support@afsplcom.com with:<br/>Order ID<br/>Product details<br/>Clear photos/videos of the issue<br/></li><li>Our team will review and respond within <strong>2–3 business days</strong><br/></li><li>If approved, we will arrange a <strong>pickup or guide you on return shipping</strong></li></ol>",
            "font_family": "sans_serif_n4",
            "font_size": 20,
            "font_size_mobile": 16,
            "font_weight": "500",
            "text_color": "#727272",
            "letter_spacing": 0,
            "word_spacing": 1,
            "text_alignment": "left",
            "margin_bottom": 30
          }
        },
        "text_block_YkDKfB": {
          "type": "text_block",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Refund Policy</p>",
            "font_family": "sans_serif_n4",
            "font_size": 30,
            "font_size_mobile": 16,
            "font_weight": "700",
            "text_color": "#727272",
            "letter_spacing": 0,
            "word_spacing": 1,
            "text_alignment": "left",
            "margin_bottom": 30
          }
        },
        "text_block_ntRh9H": {
          "type": "text_block",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Refunds will be processed under the following conditions:</p><ul><li>Return request is <strong>approved after inspection</strong></li><li>Product is received back in acceptable condition</li></ul><p>  <strong>Refund Modes:</strong></p><ul><li>Original payment method (preferred)</li><li>Bank transfer (if required)<br/></li></ul><p> <strong>Refund Timeline:</strong></p><ul><li>Initiated within <strong>5–7 business days</strong> after approval</li><li>It may take additional time depending on your bank/payment provider</li></ul>",
            "font_family": "sans_serif_n4",
            "font_size": 20,
            "font_size_mobile": 16,
            "font_weight": "500",
            "text_color": "#727272",
            "letter_spacing": 0,
            "word_spacing": 1,
            "text_alignment": "left",
            "margin_bottom": 30
          }
        },
        "text_block_UM4mXe": {
          "type": "text_block",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Replacement Policy</p>",
            "font_family": "sans_serif_n4",
            "font_size": 30,
            "font_size_mobile": 16,
            "font_weight": "700",
            "text_color": "#727272",
            "letter_spacing": 0,
            "word_spacing": 1,
            "text_alignment": "left",
            "margin_bottom": 30
          }
        },
        "text_block_pgygKW": {
          "type": "text_block",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<ul><li>In case of damaged or defective products, we may offer a <strong>replacement instead of refund</strong>, based on availability</li></ul>",
            "font_family": "sans_serif_n4",
            "font_size": 20,
            "font_size_mobile": 16,
